  "title": "Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p>We are looking for a Graphics Designer with 2 to 3 years experience in</p><p>Signage design, 3D Signages, Poster design, Flyer design , Paper Publications , Corporate Logo & design , Even Management, Hoarding design</p><p>1. Professional graphic design preferably with a creative ideas.</p><p>2. Diploma/Bachelor's degree in graphic design, art or related discipline.</p><p>3. Exceptional creativity and innovative design skills</p><p>4. Excellent communication and presentation skills.</p><p>5. Ability to manage timelines.</p><p>6. Working knowledge of various graphic design software.</p><p>7. Good attitude and passionate hunger to achieve creative goals.</p><p></p>",
