    "description": "<p>Hitech Images was established in April 2009 providing services in the inkjet printing industries. Providing Services in the Large format printing and Technology Company - Specializes in the production of Large Prints and images, posters, banners,Vehicle Stickers, Signages, LED Signages, Acrylic Cut-out Letters, Acrylic Light Box, T-Shirt Printing, Books Magazine, Website Design &amp; Hosting, Web Development, Advertisement Flim, Creative Logo Design with a range of experience in signages manufacturing.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Over years, today it is known as <strong>Hi-Tech Images Pte. Ltd.</strong> with a past proven records of producing products ranging from indoor to outdoor services. Using the latest, state of the Art Technology in Digital Printing and most current softwares, we are able to produce &amp; deliver on-time delivery with high quality image anticipating your needs &amp; exceeds your requirements.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our business set-up concept is to provide consultations &amp; professionalism services in terms of planning using high quality digital printing technology to suit your requirements. Our professional services had extended to the following industries :-</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Advertising Agencies</li>\n  <li>Design &amp; Communications House</li>\n  <li>Marketing Consultants</li>\n  <li>Exhibition Companies</li>\n  <li>Property Developers</li>\n  <li>Government &amp; Statuatories Boards</li>\n  <li>Commercial Companies</li>\n  <li>Retail Outlets</li>\n  <li>MRT &amp; LRT Trains</li>\n  <li>Vans, Trucks &amp; Buses</li>\n</ul>",
